    description:
      '<h1 class="MsoNormal">About this listing</h1>\n\n\n\n<p class="MsoNormal">Welcome aboard the 727 Fuse”lodge” at the Pilot Lodge!Available July\n    1st, 2025.</p>\n\n\n\n<p class="MsoNormal">We have 2 completed airplane homes on the property, and this will be our\n    3rd. This 727 will serve as a communal space for our guests staying in our\n    cabins and airplane homes. The 727 also has a private room where you will be\n    staying with private bathroom in the aft section of the aircraft. Your room and\n    bathroom are private, while the front part of the airplane is shared with other\n    passengers such as yourself!</p>\n\n<h3 class="MsoNormal">The space</h3>\n\n<p class="MsoNormal">The 727 is located on the north end of the property along runway 07/25.\n    You can fly in or drive in to access the property.</p>\n\n<p class="MsoNormal">This is a pre-booking option for summer of 2025 as we have two completed\n    airplane homes:<br>\n    airbnb.com/h/dc6<br>\n    and<br>\n    airbnb.com/h/dc-9/</p>\n\n<p class="MsoNormal">The regular nightly rate for the 727 private room is $399/night.</p>\n\n<p class="MsoNormal">We are currently offering a discounted rate to those who want to\n    pre-book a stay with us for the 2025 season!</p>\n\n<h3 class="MsoNormal">Guest access</h3>\n\n<p class="MsoNormal">As a 727 guest you can access the entire 727! You’ll find a communal\n    kitchen space in the forward section of the airplane as well as a lounging area\n    and fire pit!</p>\n\n<p class="MsoNormal">In the late summer and early fall you are welcome to walk around the\n    wetlands on the property and pick wild cranberries and blueberries (over 30\n    acres of berries on the property!).</p>\n\n<h3 class="MsoNormal">During your stay</h3>\n\n<p class="MsoNormal">If you need anything during your stay you can message one of our “flight\n    attendants” from 9am-6pm or reach your host via satellite text messaging from\n    6pm-11pm. (number provided when you book).</p>\n\n<h3 class="MsoNormal">Other things to note</h3>\n\n<p class="MsoNormal">Please note this is a smoke-free property and we do not allow smoking or\n    vaping anywhere on the property.</p>\n\n<p class="MsoNormal">&nbsp;<br></p>',
