    description:
      '<h2 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; outline: none; font-family: Quicksand, sans-serif; font-weight: 700; line-height: 30px; color: rgb(59, 66, 73); font-size: 20px; text-transform: none; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: left; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(247, 248, 249); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;">About this listing</h2><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; outline: none; color: rgb(59, 66, 73); font-family: Quicksand, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(247, 248, 249); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;"><br></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; outline: none; color: rgb(59, 66, 73); font-family: Quicksand, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(247, 248, 249); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;">Welcome to Lake Powell’s loveliest vacation property, located only a mile from Page Municipal Airport!</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; outline: none; color: rgb(59, 66, 73); font-family: Quicksand, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(247, 248, 249); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;">This gorgeous home was built to give you the very best Lake Powell accommodations.&nbsp; Our custom home (2000 sf) features 10’ ceilings, travertine floors, granite counter tops and all stainless steel appliances. There is also a fully furnished laundry room to take care of all your washing needs. This beautiful new home has 4 bedrooms and 3 baths, and the open floor plan makes it perfect for entertaining. Bedroom #1 has a king bed and private bath; bedroom #2 has a king bed; bedroom #3 has two full beds (bunk); bedroom #4 (casita) has 2 full beds and private bath. Bedrooms #2 and #3 share the full bath in the hallway. We have 2 master suites located on opposite sides of the home (bedrooms #1 and #4). The casita is attached to the house and has a separate entrance for maximum privacy. This home has four TVs total (a 60” in living room, two 40” in master suites and a 32” in the guest room). The home will sleep 10 people comfortably.&nbsp; Our 50-foot connected garage is perfect for your boat (garage has a 9′ tall door for larger boats) and vehicles. This home features amazing Lake Powell views as the lake is only ¾ miles away! The home also has unrestricted views of the Vermillion Cliffs which feature the most amazing sunsets every evening!</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; outline: none; color: rgb(59, 66, 73); font-family: Quicksand, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(247, 248, 249); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;">The back yard features a very large covered patio which comes complete with patio furniture and grill.&nbsp; The back courtyard also opens up into a fully landscaped 1-acre area for your enjoyment. We also have a front courtyard with an outdoor table and seating for 6.</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; outline: none; color: rgb(59, 66, 73); font-family: Quicksand, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(247, 248, 249); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;">This home is located in a very exclusive area in Lake Powell’s premiere development called Indigo Ridge. Nestled in the back of a cul-de-sac, this home offers great privacy and enjoyment. Everything about this home is brand new…furniture, linens, appliances etc.</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; outline: none; color: rgb(59, 66, 73); font-family: Quicksand, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(247, 248, 249); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;">If you enjoy walking, take in the amazing scenery of Lake Powell from the 4-mile looped trail overlooking the lake which begins a few hundred yards from this home. Weekly discounts are available. We look forward to earning your business and making your stay one you will remember. Safe travels!</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; outline: none; color: rgb(59, 66, 73); font-family: Quicksand, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(247, 248, 249); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;"><span style="color: rgb(25, 30, 59); font-family: &quot;Centra No2&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; display: inline !important; float: none;">(State of AZ Property ID: 21360145)</span></p>',
