    description:
      '<h2 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; outline: none; font-family: Quicksand, sans-serif; font-weight: 700; line-height: 30px; color: rgb(59, 66, 73); font-size: 20px; text-transform: none; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: left; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(247, 248, 249); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;">About this listing</h2><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; outline: none; color: rgb(59, 66, 73); font-family: Quicksand, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(247, 248, 249); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;"><br></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; outline: none; color: rgb(59, 66, 73); font-family: Quicksand, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(247, 248, 249); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;">Welcome to the most beautiful Valley in all of Idaho! You will be surrounded by stunning 360° views of the prettiest mountains here. We are right in the middle of Stanley, ID, and Ketchum, ID. Peaks and hikes and gorgeous lakes surround us. Our favorite lakes are Redfish Lake which boasts the most incredible backdrop–the Sawtooth Mountains’ jagged peaks; Pettit Lake, because it is beautiful and very close to us; and Alturas Lake which, true to its Spanish name meaning heights, sits an entire 20 feet higher than Pettit! LOL.</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; outline: none; color: rgb(59, 66, 73); font-family: Quicksand, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(247, 248, 249); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;">This tiny home feels anything but tiny. It is equipped with everything you would expect in a full-sized home. The bedroom boasts a king bed with a cute staircase leading up to it. Under the stairs, you will find ample storage space, a washer/dryer, and a refrigerator. The kitchen has a small stovetop, a full-size farm sink, and all the kitchen tools you need for a comfortable stay.</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; outline: none; color: rgb(59, 66, 73); font-family: Quicksand, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(247, 248, 249); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;">Windows galore make it easy to enjoy the beautiful mountain views and watch people play in the center courtyard.</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; outline: none; color: rgb(59, 66, 73); font-family: Quicksand, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(247, 248, 249); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;">Despite the abundance of windows, the near-silent climate control keeps the home at the temperature you desire.</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; outline: none; color: rgb(59, 66, 73); font-family: Quicksand, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(247, 248, 249); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;">Let us know if you need anything at all during your stay. We are here to help any time of day or night.</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; outline: none; color: rgb(59, 66, 73); font-family: Quicksand, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(247, 248, 249); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;">We are located immediately next to the Smiley Creek Airport. Just land and walk on over!</p>',
